<item>
            <title>[OAK-404] Log (slow) queries</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-404</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Queries should be logged if the log level is set to debug.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In addition to that, arguably very slow queries should be logged with level warning.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
